#-----------------------------------------
# raudio
# https://github.com/Phenomer/raudio
#-----------------------------------------

cross-platform audio library bindings for ruby1.9 

* Depend
- ruby1.9/dl
- libao
- libogg
- libvorbis
- libmpg123

* Original documents
- ruby 
  http://www.ruby-lang.org/
- libao
  http://www.xiph.org/ao/
- libogg
  http://www.xiph.org/ogg/
- libvorbis
  http://www.xiph.org/vorbis/

* Setup
sudo aptitude install libao-dev libogg-dev libvorbis-dev libmpg123-dev

